{"tid":2490154,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（國際關係基本準則）陸委會：「台灣從未屬於中华人民共和国 未來更不會」","createTime":"2021-04-15T11:25:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-15T11:30:43.000Z","uid":184679,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"095e189282996fa9f25e25aac86f784cce70b26c","tid":2490154,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T11:25:50.000Z","msg":"在台灣，陸委會嚴正抗議大陸國台辦指，國民黨在1949年退踞台灣後從此喪失代表全中國合法政府地位的講法。陸委會發言人邱垂正表示，台灣從未屬於中華人民共和國，未來更不會，強調這是根據國際法原則的歷史事實與現實，不是中共單方面片面主張所能改變。他說，中共如果以消滅台灣作為兩岸關係發展的終點，以軍事威嚇、強加政治框架，要求台灣屈從，台灣絕不會接受。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/china/2387388\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Fchina%2F2387388&d=Uh5SjXth0XRRLWSKrhPNwPzGhZJjjhZ%2BTSWVZI8Eykc%3D&h=7a72e8a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/china/2387388</a>"},{"pid":"1a8d795d5d66f7f098f47d6a710ed8e4909758dd","tid":2490154,"uid":17641,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T11:26:53.000Z","msg":"台灣係屬於日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31915ba3fbef98228f4802b47479eb00fdb8b269","tid":2490154,"uid":310700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a8d795d5d66f7f098f47d6a710ed8e4909758dd","tid":2490154,"uid":17641,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T11:26:53.000Z","msg":"台灣係屬於日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T11:28:14.000Z","msg":"老納呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8eb74ecdacc9766237b26fecc2f9ddf444c71cc7","tid":2490154,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T11:28:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支那狗最近靜左<br />\n千祈唔好死狗呀"},{"pid":"ec09ac38b2e6b6f3a6238be3408ad96a18229baa","tid":2490154,"uid":228894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T11:29:33.000